CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 21, 1956, page A1, reads: "OES Committee for the grand affair held during the 39th annual session of Deborah Grand Chapter OES PHA, included, front, Ruth Tucker, Charles Jones, Ella Mae Phillips. Rear: Vera Winslow, Virginia Valentine and Juanita Saunders. - 'Teenie' Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of man wearing dark suit, bow tie, and eyeglasses, and five women wearing light colored dresses and ribbons, including one in center also wearing floral sash, posed in front of stairs for the 39th annual session of Deborah Grand Chapter OES PHA
